## .NET build output
bin/
obj/

## User-specific VS files
*.user
*.suo
.vs/

## Serilog log files
*.log

## Published output
publish/
*.zip
meshcom-webclient-*.zip
out/

## Rider
.idea/

## OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## Certificates (never commit private keys)
certs/*.pfx
certs/*.p12
certs/*.key
certs/*.pem

## Settings override written by SettingsService at runtime
**/appsettings.override.json

## Runtime data files (generated at runtime, not part of source)
**/data/

## Installer build artifacts (generated by build-windows-installer.ps1 / CI)
installer/publish/
installer/output/

## License generation tools (private keys – NEVER commit!)
tools/private/
tools/private/*.key
tools/private/*.pem
